{"tid":2075321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧：要求中國立即釋放加拿大公民康明凱及邁克爾","createTime":"2020-06-22T19:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T00:25:47.000Z","uid":53844,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"935acd75eafaa3fe097328772cb6cb63cdaf89c3","tid":2075321,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:05:01.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧表示，美方極度關切兩人的案件，批評中方的指控有政治動機，毫無根據。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在聲明中表示，美國和加拿大立場一致，要求北京立即釋放兩人，美方反對中方利用這種不正當的扣押方法，來脅迫加拿大。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大總理杜魯多對蓬佩奧所發的聲明表示感謝，認為加拿大的盟友都非常關注案件，現時必需團結一致，因為類似的事件可能會發生在其他國家的公民身上。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-23 02:53:19<br />\n<br />\nRTHK NEWS"},{"pid":"ed1213e4e19d4660e7c627caf2e27cd9b79f57d2","tid":2075321,"uid":37586,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:07:03.000Z","msg":"準備出師有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3cf18da03e4a1f507991c7917d7fa6a67c08ce","tid":2075321,"uid":88134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:07:24.000Z","msg":"你叫Justin Trudeau仲點出嚟行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e896de06020e766af8999294cfc960e2d8700c7","tid":2075321,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f3cf18da03e4a1f507991c7917d7fa6a67c08ce","tid":2075321,"uid":88134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:07:24.000Z","msg":"你叫Justin Trudeau仲點出嚟行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:08:05.000Z","msg":"大佬出手"},{"pid":"401c656aec5b9ac612d4b0a45a50db60bf516ece","tid":2075321,"uid":88134,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4e896de06020e766af8999294cfc960e2d8700c7","tid":2075321,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f3cf18da03e4a1f507991c7917d7fa6a67c08ce","tid":2075321,"uid":88134,