5.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71eb7e68d7693e8eedb5de7a52aa5964a81f1c94","tid":2075321,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"401c656aec5b9ac612d4b0a45a50db60bf516ece","tid":2075321,"uid":88134,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4e896de06020e766af8999294cfc960e2d8700c7","tid":2075321,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f3cf18da03e4a1f507991c7917d7fa6a67c08ce","tid":2075321,"uid":88134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:07:24.000Z","msg":"你叫Justin Trudeau仲點出嚟行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:08:05.000Z","msg":"大佬出手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:11:02.000Z","msg":"加拿大公民被中國無理輯拿<br />\n然後竟然係由美國出面施壓<br />\n大佬你加拿大同支那個貿易額又唔係巨大到好似美國咁<br />\n洗唔洗咁驚支那呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:13:26.000Z","msg":"沉默的20秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fe7935717272fa7c9e922c65d29d3df78df54a","tid":2075321,"uid":88134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:14:18.000Z","msg":"btw, 其實香港應該係有大約接近30萬有加拿大籍<br />\n呢批人自己小心啦<br />\n支那共匪要捉人質一定捉呢啲先<br />\n唔係加拿大洗乜出份歡迎加籍公民回家既聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d64d260dfdbfa44ce90637d127c89eee765d3d","tid":2075321,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:15:49.000Z","msg":"哦 你死喇支那 老美第一次就呢單野強硬出聲"},{"pid":"704ca7f1f087c0c8f3020277ccb1839e1748ea6c","tid":2075321,"uid":33614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:16:55.000Z","msg":"加拿大個總理同自由黨係中國身上拎左唔小油水<br />\n上年中國國慶加拿大升中國國旗 我就知無撚得救<br />\n所以唔好覺得加拿大會還擊 佢地無實力同本錢去做"},{"pid":"451b2823ddeef138474b9ff6fe6a2e6ab651de56","tid":2075321,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"