 red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:30:22.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\nBoris Johnson同佢都係一擔擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無話邊個差過邊個<br />\n香港問題，我公道啲講<br />\n佢的確唔需要為3,40年前mrs. thatcher既決定負責任，所以暫且撇開唔講<br />\n但canzuk又係佢話要搞既<br />\n明知澳洲人早就已經有走向共和既傾向，係意識形態上同經濟上都根本唔撚想同你有freedom of movement既協議<br />\n早排澳洲森林大火都只係得女皇陞下一封慰問信<br />\n法國都識得話可以派消防去幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家因為話要搞武漢肺炎獨立調查就被支那制裁農產品，又係美國出聲聲援<br />\n我係加拿大澳洲都親美親歐好過親英啦下話？<br />\n返返嚟香港，本土派頭號敵人黎智英咪英籍架囉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4330abf6f1041881d59cdedde8d4206947f4ef","tid":2075321,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91e80c1d029a7e50de8346dd4d824ebed48fe2b6","tid":2075321,"uid":256837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:18:20.000Z","msg":"加拿大外長逢中就軟 被踢爆向中國銀行借近4000萬房貸<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2060646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2060646</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:51:50.000Z","msg":"加拿大11bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a60ed81fa1ae63a97487c154d374e7a4abb534","tid":2075321,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f3cf18da03e4a1f507991c7917d7fa6a67c08ce","tid":2075321,"uid":88134,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:07:24.000Z","msg":"你叫Justin Trudeau仲點出嚟行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:56:19.000Z","msg":"你想佢點？放撚左孟晚舟交換囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af900d4eb4c8e58523cefd5d599fd7927fb27e69","tid":2075321,"uid":3515